<plot>'Ghost Town' is a short drama based on Dante's Inferno. Blake and Haily, a modern Bonnie and Clyde couple, find themselves in a ghost town somewhere in the middle of nowhere after something went wrong during their last robbery. The couple has died and now Blake and Haily are trapped in a ghost town, representing Dante's seventh circle of hell, the circle of the violent. Their punishment is to relive the same day over and over again - the day they died.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?214255</url></doc>
